{"tid":912893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺戲院講嘢冇問題？","createTime":"2018-11-23T04:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T05:43:40.000Z","uid":219546,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e2276f1ee0e6c0ed5d38c69fa27d41a142dbe1","tid":912893,"uid":219546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱一個人去戲院睇戲嗰陣，隔離坐咗對疑似abc嘅情侶，由坐低已經開始中英夾雜咁傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始一句起兩句止我都算，但去到中場嗰陣佢哋連續傾咗成分鐘，咁我真喺頂唔順，就用英文同佢哋講喺戲院唔可以講嘢，請佢哋真喺要講嘢都盡量細聲小小<br />\n點知，嗰嗰男仔大大聲鬧番我轉頭，仲話我喺bitch，話我咁鍾意靜點解唔番屋企自己睇碟，之後仲話你唔鍾意可以走，然後佢哋成場戲都繼續旁若無人咁講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明佢哋前後左右都坐滿哂人，大家都俾佢哋影響到，但喺點解去到中場都冇人肯/敢出聲，就算我出完聲俾人鬧番轉頭，都冇人幫我講過一句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真喺好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad1295d30f035df289504a93d8cb819a7947dc3","tid":912893,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"叫佢地返屋企扑野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39c0fe31f4522827bbb14a54c06b5a181c4e1ef","tid":912893,"uid":166827,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"渣ga，你唔識繼續屌鳩佢？唔係就叫職員啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a68d3abbaa4ff43ecbc487af0ccf71250c0e3c","tid":912893,"uid":219546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39c0fe31f4522827bbb14a54c06b5a181c4e1ef","tid":912893,"uid":166827,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"渣ga，你唔識繼續屌鳩佢？唔係就叫職員啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"嗰男人望落去好大份，而我只係一個弱質又毒嘅女仔，出聲已經用咗好大勇氣<img src=\"/asset